3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes a new approach for generating videos based on semantic meaning, which is a key area of research in AI. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with generating videos, which is a common topic in computer graphics research. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with generating videos from semantic label maps, which is a common topic in multimedia research.
